Setup Redux :
$ npm install redux react-redux
$ npm install redux-logger
$ npm install axios redux-thunk

//for router install react-router-dom 
$ npm install react-router-dom

1. install redux devtools
add extension to crome
2. https://github.com/zalmoxisus/redux-devtools-extension
goto uses section ->goto 1.3 Use redux-devtools-extension package from npm
$ npm install --save redux-devtools-extension

3.install in store.js file
import { composeWithDevTools } from 'redux-devtools-extension';
in store.js file
4.const store = createStore(rootReducer, composeWithDevTools(applyMiddleware(logger)))

5. how to make API calls with redux
two packages need to install
(i)axios (request to an API end point)
(ii)redux-thunk (define async action creator)

6.$ npm install axios redux-thunk

7. install react-icons
npm install react-icons --save

8.install redux-form
npm install --save redux-form

